Day 7:

Take the ITIL Foundation exam!
This is just a suggested plan, and you may need to adjust it based on your own learning style and schedule. However, if you follow this plan, you should be well-prepared to pass the ITIL Foundation exam.

Here are some additional tips for learning the key topics:

Use a variety of resources to learn the material. There are many books, websites, and online courses available.
Find a study partner or group to help you stay motivated and accountable.
Don't be afraid to ask questions. There are many people who are willing to help you learn the material.
